name: LR-Cum in stomach
description:
LR-Cum in stomach

A lora for generate [cum in stomach] content base on AOM3.

  • Use the weights in 0.6~0.8.

  • View the parameters in my sample, you can refer to the prompts, in general, "cum in stomach" should be include.

  • Others oral prompt could be used to prove the effect (but actually, I don't know how effective it'll be).

  • Add negpormpt “censored, cunsore bar”to avoid censor,as far as posible...

  • Still some problem, like overfitting or censored, may be solved in the future.

That's all.

Only 1version this time. Mainly because the effect is not very good，I gotta do somemore...
